-thi%C3%AAn-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Ba-v%C4%83n/poem-mgYAjQ2Q5NsDGZNtKtk96w">Tế thiên địa văn - 祭天地文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/T%E1%BA%BF-tr%E1%BA%ADn-vong/poem-JnHWJb5Kd6-M07NFz1l5Zw">Tế trận vong - 祭陣亡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-Vi-t%E1%BA%A3-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-zYImYpb82xchstT0tz3scQ">Thướng Vi tả tướng nhị thập vận - 上韋左相二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Linh/T%E1%BB%ADu-%C4%91%E1%BB%A9c-t%E1%BB%A5ng/poem-J13HP-vW93XWQ7-28U2Z0A">Tửu đức tụng - 酒德頌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Linh/author-hkIbirWYM3zvfGsJ_u2tHQ">Lưu Linh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
